{"tid":2126852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息：行會通過食肆全日禁堂食　周三凌晨生效","createTime":"2020-07-27T05:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T05:46:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3be583609d911c6be46dcc4cbeb0ff626ea378c4","tid":2126852,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:17:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540080-20200727.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540080-20200727.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=7848fbeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540080-20200727.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a948258e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540080-20200727.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n消息指出，政府下午將公布收緊防疫措施，食肆將全日禁止堂食，以及強制市民在室外也要戴口罩，飲食期間可豁免，新措施星期三凌晨生效。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，政府與超級市場集團商討，在超市實施自願加強防疫措施，另外政府轄下的街市亦會加強防疫。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議早上召開特別會議討論，並通過有關安排。"},{"pid":"773893da7b9b747324a308df26cddda34dafb7b5","tid":2126852,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:18:00.000Z","msg":"船主協會累死咗飲食業<br />\n<br />\n我建議應該向船主協會會員抽懲罰性稅<br />\n去補償返比飲食業"},{"pid":"ccf046091f8d764512b51ef6c06de2ba52abf6fd","tid":2126852,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:46:42.000Z","msg":"茶樓可以執定粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝船東會及董建華一齊攬炒藍色經濟"}]}